: 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "64397": {"data": {"tag_id": 64397, "tag_name": "微电影", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/51421ea8bdd2fe616d50f2711a1e58b67361850d.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "微电影（Micro film），即微型电影，又称微影。微电影是指专门运用在各种新媒体平台上播放的、适合在移动状态和短时休闲状态下观看的、具有完整策划和系统制作体系支持的具有完整故事情节的视频（“类”电影）短片，内容融合了幽默搞怪、时尚潮流、公益教育、商业定制等主题，可以单独成篇，也可系列成剧。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "2947": {"data": {"tag_id": 2947, "tag_name": "特摄", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/11d6f73281947ac0d0371897241ad9ef5530b6b6.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "13784": {"data": {"tag_id": 13784, "tag_name": "迪迦奥特曼", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/5849230d7d6a7802512531fd91304625bfff001a.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "迪迦在印度尼西亚语中，代表了神圣的数字&amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;3&amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;。大约三千万年以前，地球处于超古代，奇杰拉花朵盛开，邪神加坦杰厄降临，巨人们发生内战，原是地球最强的黑暗战士迪迦在受幽怜的感动后化为光，使其黑暗力量长眠。但超古代文明并没有因此而得救，人们全部都迷上了奇杰拉花的花粉，因为光之巨人无法干涉人类的选择，所以巨人把自己战斗的躯体隐藏在金字塔后，化作光离开了地球", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "1113118": {"data": {"tag_id": 1113118, "tag_name": "ULTRAMAN TIGA", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute"